140
00:18:30,501 --> 00:18:33,665
- You're an American.
- That's right.

141
00:18:33,665 --> 00:18:36,829
- My uncle was born in America.
- Really?

142
00:18:36,829 --> 00:18:39,705
But he was one of the lucky ones.

143
00:18:39,705 --> 00:18:44,692
He managed to escape in a balloon
during the Jimmy Carter presidency.

144
00:18:44,692 --> 00:18:47,568
- I bet he's got a lot of great stories.
- Yes!

145
00:18:47,568 --> 00:18:51,884
